divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home and i saw a flashing light, once i got home i was standing outside of my car, talking to a friend. Then i looked up and saw two circle, disc shaped objects flying just above the tree tops. They had 6 dull green lights around the base and flew slowly. They were very quiet, but had a light humming sound. Once they passed, i didnt see them again.
